Metadata-Version: 2.1
Name: onegov.chat
Version: 0.2.1
Summary: Chat messages for OneGov Cloud.
Home-page: http://github.com/OneGov/onegov.chat
Author: Seantis GmbH
Author-email: info@seantis.ch
License: GPLv2
Description: 
        
        Run the Tests
        -------------
            
        Install tox and run it::
        
            pip install tox
            tox
        
        Limit the tests to a specific python version::
        
            tox -e py27
        
        Conventions
        -----------
        
        Onegov Chat follows PEP8 as close as possible. To test for it run::
        
            tox -e pep8
        
        Onegov Chat uses `Semantic Versioning <http://semver.org/>`_
        
